SUMMARY:RFC6638 Scheduling Properties Test Event

ORGANIZER;CN=Alice Organizer;
 SCHEDULE-AGENT=SERVER;
 SCHEDULE-FORCE-SEND=REQUEST:
 mailto:alice@example.com

ATTENDEE;CN=Bob Attendee;
 ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;
 PARTSTAT=NEEDS-ACTION;
 RSVP=TRUE;
 SCHEDULE-AGENT=CLIENT;
 SCHEDULE-FORCE-SEND=REQUEST;
 SCHEDULE-STATUS="1.2":
 mailto:bob@example.com

ATTENDEE;CN=Carol Attendee;
 ROLE=OPT-PARTICIPANT;
 PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;
 SCHEDULE-AGENT=SERVER;
 SCHEDULE-FORCE-SEND=REPLY;
 SCHEDULE-STATUS="2.0;Success":
 mailto:carol@example.com

ATTENDEE;CN=Dave Attendee;
 ROLE=NON-PARTICIPANT;
 PARTSTAT=DECLINED;
 SCHEDULE-AGENT=NONE;
 SCHEDULE-STATUS="5.1;Service unavailable":
 mailto:dave@example.com

DESCRIPTION:This event is used to unit test parsing of RFC6638 scheduling parameters.
